Object        Field            Charset
------------+----------------+------------------------
Library     | Name           | URI-Restricted
------------+----------------+------------------------
User        | LibraryName    | URI-Restricted
User        | FirstName      | UTF-8
User        | LastName       | UTF-8
User        | UserName       | URI-Restricted
User        | EmployeeNumber | Numeric
User        | MailAddress    | UTF-8
User        | ExternalID     | UTF-8
------------+----------------+------------------------
Team        | LibraryName    | URI-Restricted
Team        | TeamName       | URI-Restricted
Team        | ExternalID     | UTF-8
------------+----------------+------------------------

Numeric         0-9
URI-Restricted  abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ0123456789-_.

Absolute addressing of identities:
  schema:   LibraryName~UserName
  example:  ui~jpernfuss
